{"id":"5a374d69-8d62-407a-aec5-9c08148ff3e0","name":"Tide","description":"<p>🧜‍♂️ | During a ranging tropical storm, Tide is worried about how you are faring -- even if he hates humans.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_8c22eede-16b0-4231-ab95-7fc57411bc73.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_dcda1904-fdf5-4799-b828-16f2f3e4f439.webp?width=1000\">Hello! Yes! He's 26 feet! I wanted to make him BIG!! But mostly it's just his tail length, which is 21 feet. Oarfish are so fascinating, did you know in some areas of the world, an oarfish washing up can mean future natural disasters or as a warning sign in some cultures?</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_3b9cb5d6-95b3-4a2d-abfe-c827e8bd8be8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>That being said, if you are in Florida (like me!) Please be safe during Tropical Storm Debbie!</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_035d8022-daa8-447b-abb2-0d51fa98ed23.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_d90d34c2-93b8-4003-870d-6819f049d449.webp","creator":"gunko","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦄 Non-human","🧖 Giant","🧬 Demi-Human","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":3051,"messages":31886,"created_at":"2024-08-04T20:05:20.063467+00:00"}